comments: There is also a Kamrup in the dataset. Not sure if that should be included.
There is Bangalore Rural district in the dataset. Maybe what we have is Bangalore Urban. But I am unsure as to whether both of them are included in the NCAP.
I am assuming that "Mumbai" is "Mumbai Suburban" and "Navi Mumbai" is "Mumbai City".
Is Dera Baba, another name for Pathankot?
There is also a Kanpur Nagar in Uttar Pradesh, but I have not taken that.
